<!DOCTYPE html>

<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Laundry Service Order Form</title>

```
<style>
    *{
        box-sizing:border-box;
        margin:0;
        padding:0;
    }

    body{
        font-family:Arial,sans-serif;
        background-color:#f2f2f2;
    }

   .navbar{
    position:fixed;
    top:0;
    left:0;
    width:100%;
    height:90px;
    background:#fff;

    display:flex;
    align-items:center;
    justify-content:space-between;

    padding:0 40px;

    box-shadow:0 2px 10px rgba(0,0,0,.1);

    z-index:1000;
}

    #logo{
        height:60px;
        margin-right:50px;
    }

    .nav-links{
    display:flex;
    align-items:center;
    gap:20px;
}

    .navbar a{
        font-size:22px;
        margin-right:20px;
        color:black;
        text-decoration:none;
        font-weight:700;
    }

    .navbar a:hover{
        color:#3ca22c;
        text-decoration:underline;
    }

    #profile{
    border-radius:20px;
    padding:12px 25px;
    background-color:#3ca22c;
    color:white !important;
}

    .content{
        margin-top:130px;
    }

    .container{
        width:80%;
        margin:30px auto;
        background-color:#fff;
        border-radius:10px;
        padding:30px;
        box-shadow:0 0 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
    }

    h1{
        color:#2c7a22;
        text-align:center;
        margin-bottom:30px;
    }

    .form-group{
        margin-bottom:20px;
    }

    label{
        display:block;
        font-weight:bold;
        margin-bottom:5px;
    }

    input[type="number"]{
        width:100%;
        padding:10px;
        font-size:16px;
        border:1px solid #ccc;
        border-radius:5px;
    }

    button{
        display:block;
        width:100%;
        padding:12px;
        background-color:#3ca22c;
        color:#fff;
        border:none;
        border-radius:5px;
        font-size:18px;
        cursor:pointer;
        transition:0.3s;
    }

    button:hover{
        background-color:#2c7a22;
    }

    .container7{
        background-color:#022d1aeb;
        text-align:right;
        margin-top:40px;
    }

    .container7 img{
        max-width:100%;
    }
</style>
```

</head>

<body>

```
<div class="navbar">
    <img src="/images/logo.png" id="logo">
    <div class="nav-links">
    <a href="/">Home</a>
    <a href="/about">About</a>
    <a href="/service">Services</a>
    <a href="/contact">Contact</a>
    <% if(islogin){ %>

    <a href="/profile">Profile</a>

    <a href="/order">Order</a>

    <a href="/myorders">My Orders</a>

    <% if(role === "admin"){ %>
        <a href="/admin">Admin</a>
    <% } %>

    <a href="/logout" id="profile">Logout</a>

<% } else { %>

    <a href="/login" id="profile">
        Login/Signup
    </a>

<% } %>
</div>
</div>
<div class="content">

    <div class="container">

        <h1>Prepare Your Order!</h1>

        <form action="/submit-order" method="POST">

            <div class="form-group">
                <label for="shirt">Shirts (₹10 each)</label>
                <input type="number" id="shirt" name="shirt" min="0" step="1" value="0">
            </div>

            <div class="form-group">
                <label for="pants">Pants (₹10 each)</label>
                <input type="number" id="pants" name="pants" min="0" step="1" value="0">
            </div>

            <div class="form-group">
                <label for="socks">Socks (₹2 each)</label>
                <input type="number" id="socks" name="socks" min="0" step="1" value="0">
            </div>

            <div class="form-group">
                <label for="saree">Sarees (₹12 each)</label>
                <input type="number" id="saree" name="saree" min="0" step="1" value="0">
            </div>

            <div class="form-group">
                <label for="jacket">Jackets (₹15 each)</label>
                <input type="number" id="jacket" name="jacket" min="0" step="1" value="0">
            </div>

            <div class="form-group">
                <label for="suit">Suits (₹15 each)</label>
                <input type="number" id="suit" name="suit" min="0" step="1" value="0">
            </div>

            <div class="form-group">
                <label for="other">Other Clothes (₹8 each)</label>
                <input type="number" id="other" name="other" min="0" step="1" value="0">
            </div>

            <button type="submit">Place Order</button>

        </form>

    </div>

    <div class="container7">
        <img src="/images/Screenshot 2024-03-28 165716.png" alt="Footer Image">
    </div>

</div>
```

</body>
</html>
